OK, now what are you waiting for?!!?!

Start Ineptris (if you only have 2 meg mem, close all other programs first).
Make sure you have Inept mode >ON<, select >START GAME<, and PLAY PLAY PLAY!

If there is something you don't understand check out the guide.




And remember..                     >>>MAILWARE<<<
